item.title: CVE-2018-14800|2024-09-17T00:56:00.140Z -- delta%20electronics -- ispsoft
item.description: Delta Electronics ISPSoft version 3.0.5 and prior allow an attacker, by opening a crafted file, to cause the application to read past the boundary allocated to a stack object, which could allow execution of code under the context of the application.
